snippet.title: Soul's Remnant 2022 Playtest Trailer
snippet.description:
Play Soul's Remnant for free during the 2022 playtest, starting December 16th at 8 PM eastern time.

Make an account on the game's website to be ready to play on December 16th: https://soulsremnant.com

Join the Soul's Remnant Discord to stay updated on the project and when the game goes live: https://discord.gg/soulsremnant

Soul's Remnant made and owned by Chaomoon
https://chaomoon.com
